title: The Stickit minister :
author: Crockett, S. R.
snippet: " Na," said Rob, seriously ; " it's for Tarn M'Kittrick o' the Gallaberry.

title: The Stickit minister :
author: Crockett, S. R.
snippet: " Stan' up, then, Tam M'Kittrick frae the Gallaberry,  for I'm gaun to gie ye the best lickin' ye ever got in your life ! "
